长夜漫漫啊
You look like you had a long night.

04:43.800 --> 04:44.600
没错
Yeah.

04:45.900 --> 04:48.400
我花了很久喂老鼠吃巧克力
I spent most of it feeding chocolate to a rat.

04:48.500 --> 04:51.100
