I don't have a whole lot to work with these days.

04:52.500 --> 04:55.000
她拿走了那本书 鸟类导读
She's got the book, man, the bird guide.

04:55.800 --> 04:57.000
她发现了
She worked it out.

04:57.000 --> 04:58.600
那我们手上没有筹码了
So we have no leverage.

04:58.900 --> 04:59.790
-没了 -告诉我
-No. -Tell me

04:59.800 --> 05:02.390
当你递上那本书的时候
When you were handing over the book,

05:02.400 --> 05:05.290
你有没有要LJ和莎拉的最新照片
did you ask for a recent photo of LJ and Sara?

05:05.300 --> 05:06.100
是的
Yeah.

05:06.800 --> 05:08.100
那照片呢?
