Man, I'm not in a position to bargain with these people.

05:12.500 --> 05:13.800
我是说他们已经被激怒了
I mean, they're pissed.

05:14.100 --> 05:15.300
明天就得越狱出来
You break out tomorrow.

05:15.400 --> 05:16.890
让我们只关注越狱一事吧
Let's just focus on that.

05:16.900 --> 05:18.200
回到正题上来
Let's keep on track.

05:19.700 --> 05:20.500
好吧
All right.

05:23.100 --> 05:24.190
当我在狱内开工的时候
While I'm working from the inside,

05:24.200 --> 05:25.590
我需要你去准备下
I need you to take care of what happens

05:25.600 --> 05:26.890
逃出来后的事宜
once we're outside.

05:26.900 --> 05:28.190
需要辆车逃之夭夭
We're going to need a getaway vehicle,

05:28.200 --> 05:30.100
不惹眼的那种
something inconspicuous.

05:30.100 --> 05:31.390
不管你找到什么车 明天下午3点
Whatever you find, it has to be parked

05:31.400 --> 05:33.590
必须停在离这半英里的地方
a half mile from here by 3:00 p.m. tomorrow.

05:33.600 --> 05:33.790
你是说凌晨3点?
You mean a.m.

05:33.800 --> 05:35.500
不 确实是下午
No, I mean p.m.

05:37.300 --> 05:38.900
林肯 我们没得选
We don't have a choice, Linc.

05:39.300 --> 05:40.990
昨晚上我做了些测试
I ran some tests last night.

05:41.000 --> 05:43.400
军方吉普车夜晚在周边巡逻
Military jeeps patrol the perimeter at night.

05:43.500 --> 05:46.000
晚上根本无法分辨他们在什么方位
There's no way of telling where they're going to be in the dark.

05:46.300 --> 05:47.900
整晚上他们都在外面巡逻
They were out there all night.

05:48.800 --> 05:50.900
我们需要夜幕遮掩 不能就
We need the dark, we can't just Just

05:51.300 --> 05:52.200
拜托别争了
Please.

05:54.000 --> 05:55.600
因为明天就要动手了
Because we're doing this tomorrow.

05:56.600 --> 05:57.800
中午时分行动
In the middle of the day.

06:22.900 --> 06:24.000
你看谁呢?
Who're you looking at?

06:24.700 --> 06:25.900
那家伙
That guy.

06:29.900 --> 06:31.100
我认识他
I know him.

07:10.850 --> 07:13.240
小麦迪朋友 我需要块手表
McGrady, my friend, I'm going to need a watch.

07:13.250 --> 07:14.450
或许要2块
Maybe two.

07:14.950 --> 07:16.450
我不会问其中原因了
I'm not even going to ask why.

07:17.850 --> 07:20.650
我还需要些双筒望远镜
I'm also going to need some binoculars.

07:22.250 --> 07:23.750
老威廉倒是有个
Old Guillermo has a pair.

07:24.350 --> 07:26.250
他根本不可能卖给你
There's no way he'll sell them to you, man.

07:26.250 --> 07:27.840
但是望远镜也不算难搞定
But they shouldn't be hard to get.

07:27.850 --> 07:29.450
我上哪里能找到他?
Where can I find this guy?

07:51.350 --> 07:52.850
我们明天行动
We leave tomorrow.

07:58.350 --> 07:59.450
这个
This

08:04.950 --> 08:06.750
这是我们逃离索纳监狱的方案
This is how we're getting out of Sona.

08:06.850 --> 08:08.440
逃出监狱隔栏
Getting out of the cell block

08:08.450 --> 08:09.240
应该不是什么问题
shouldn't be a problem.

08:09.250 --> 08:11.050
围壁栅栏很容易突破
The grate and bars are weak,

08:11.150 --> 08:12.140
但是我们需要些绳索
but we're going to need some kind of rope,

08:12.150 --> 08:14.750
还有梯子 这样可以从另外边下去
some kind of ladder, to let us down on the other side.

08:15.250 --> 08:16.440
那就是我标出最安全的线路
That's why I figured out the safest

08:16.450 --> 08:18.350
从这里到栅栏的那个洞的原因
line from here to the hole in the fence.

08:18.450 --> 08:19.850
我们白天动手
We do it in the day,

08:19.850 --> 08:22.350
只有塔楼上的2个警卫能看到我们
we'll only be visible to the two guard towers.

08:22.550 --> 08:24.450
周边警卫的情况很难说
The perimeter guards are less predictable,

08:24.950 --> 08:26.240
但是他们只有在晚上才出没
but they're only on at night.

08:26.250 --> 08:28.340
大白天的穿越监狱逃跑?
Scurrying across the field in the middle of the day?

08:28.350 --> 08:29.350
这是唯一避开巡逻吉普车的方法
It's the only way to avoid the jeep patrol.

08:30.650 --> 08:33.350
明天下午2点 监狱大院里会有场球赛
Now, in the yard tomorrow, there's a soccer game at 2:00.

08:33.350 --> 08:35.640
应该会吸引狱内很多注意力
That should prove some distraction inside.

08:35.650 --> 08:37.240
昨天我们在挖洞的时候
And yesterday when we were digging,

08:37.250 --> 08:39.340
我看到太阳光照射到这个家伙
I saw the glare from the sun hit this guy

08:39.350 --> 08:40.850
在晌午时分
in the late afternoon.

08:41.150 --> 08:42.540
看上去他就会转身
Looked like he turned away,

08:42.550 --> 08:44.250
好似视线受阻似的
like maybe his vision was blocked.

08:44.250 --> 08:45.550
这样还不足以越狱
It's not much of a break.

08:45.750 --> 08:47.640
不 但这是唯一的方法
No, but it is

08:47.650 --> 08:49.750
我们必须这么去做
one way to do what we need to do.

08:49.750 --> 08:51.240
还有个警卫
As far as thisther guard,

08:51.250 --> 08:53.150
必须找出他的弱点
his weakness has yet to be termined.

08:57.350 --> 09:00.050
如果我们要和这帮警卫周旋
If we're going to get around these guys,

09:00.550 --> 09:02.150
就必须得了解他们
we've got to get to know them.

09:04.850 --> 09:06.550
这可没这么简单
It's not going to be easy.

09:06.950 --> 09:08.540
只有一条正真意义上的路通往监狱
There's only one real road that goes to the prison.

09:08.550 --> 09:10.950
我们不走大路 不用考虑了
We don't want a real road that's not an option.

09:17.550 --> 09:18.650
怎么了?
What?

09:18.850 --> 09:20.550
留给你兄弟的时间所剩无几
Your brother's cutting it close.

09:21.250 --> 09:21.840
你说一周的
You said a week.

09:21.850 --> 09:23.840
明天就周三了 可没空闲犯错了
Tomorrow's Wednesday, you didn't leave much room for error.

09:23.850 --> 09:25.550
根本不会犯什么错
There's not going to be an"error."

09:25.850 --> 09:27.340
听着 我有一堆事要处理 还要
Listen, I've got a lot of stuff to do and I just

09:27.350 --> 09:29.340
那就是为何我不会浪费你的时间
Which is why I won't waste your time.

09:29.350 --> 09:30.940
当惠斯勒出来后 我需要
When Whistler's free, I need to get to him

09:30.950 --> 09:31.640
立刻见到他
as soon as possible.

09:31.650 --> 09:33.040
我还在为他们逃出栅栏后
I'm still trying to work out what's going

09:33.050 --> 09:34.850
可能发生的事情忙活着
to happen once they get past the fence.

09:35.150 --> 09:37.540
一旦我知道所有细节 我会让你
Once I know all the details, I'll let you

09:37.550 --> 09:38.440
林肯 冷静
Lincoln, calm down.

09:38.450 --> 09:39.640
你让我觉得
It sounds to me like you

09:39.650 --> 09:41.350
你们两兄弟似乎有点焦头烂额
and your brother are in over your heads.

09:42.650 --> 09:44.950
莎拉的事 很抱歉
There's a bad joke about Sara somewhere in there.

09:45.450 --> 09:46.750
听着
Listen

09:48.050 --> 09:49.840
我会把详情都告诉你的
I'll let you know all the details

09:49.850 --> 09:51.850
我一知道就会打电话给你
