LJ 很好 你还有34个小时
LJ's fine. You have 34 hours.

10:03.850 --> 10:05.150
她说什么了?
What did she say?

10:06.350 --> 10:07.840
都是些废话
Nothing we don't already know.

10:07.850 --> 10:09.750
走吧 有好多事要做呢
Let's get out of here; we got a lot of stuff to do.

10:19.750 --> 10:21.250
瑞弗拉先生么?
Seir Rivera?

10:22.350 --> 10:23.550
谁?
Who?

10:23.750 --> 10:26.750
你是约格·瑞弗拉对吗?
You're Jorge Rivera, right?

10:26.750 --> 10:28.750
索纳监狱的挖墓人?
Gravedigger at Sona?

10:29.150 --> 10:30.340
什么事?
so?

10:30.350 --> 10:32.250
要搭便车吗?
Would you like a ride?

10:33.450 --> 10:36.050
