5000美金
five thousand dollars.

11:06.750 --> 11:08.140
5000美金?
Five thousand dollars?

11:08.150 --> 11:09.750
就一次?
For just one time?

11:09.850 --> 11:11.750
难道你不想干?
Couldn't you do that?

11:12.150 --> 11:14.150
我想你能办到的
I think you could do it.

11:14.750 --> 11:16.450
