In this?

11:17.250 --> 11:18.650
你疯了
You're crazy

11:18.850 --> 11:21.550
只有你可以做到
Only you can do it.

11:46.050 --> 11:47.850
我不会让他们知道的
I wouldn't let 'em see you do that.

11:50.350 --> 11:50.840
谁?
Who?

11:50.850 --> 11:52.740
任何人 这是用来喝的
Anyone. It's a drinking fountain.

11:52.750 --> 11:54.140
他们直接用嘴喝的
They put their lips right on there.

11:54.150 --> 11:56.050
你会感觉就像美酒那样
You'd think it spits straight Jack Daniels.

11:57.750 --> 11:59.750
知道怎么回事吗?
You understand what happened, don't you?

11:59.850 --> 12:02.250
你就是 这里所谓的 贱民
You're a what's-it-called? a pariah.

12:03.450 --> 12:04.840
我当初来时也犯了同样的错误
I made the same mistake when I walked in here

12:04.850 --> 12:06.040
想要保住我的钱包
tried to hang on to my wallet.

12:06.050 --> 12:08.640
接下来那两天 我可够惨的
Next thing I knew, I spent the next two days kneecap deep

12:08.650 --> 12:10.350
