I'm not hungry.

12:17.350 --> 12:18.750
会饿的
Yeah, you will be.

12:20.750 --> 12:22.350
我看到了别的美国人
I saw the other Americans.

12:22.550 --> 12:24.440
你们没人打过电话给大使馆 是吧?
So none of you have called the embassy, huh?

12:24.450 --> 12:26.340
我们这些外国佬并不都是蠢蛋
Us gringos ain't all butt buddies.

12:26.350 --> 12:28.650
要么? 不拿我就自己留着了
You want it? Cause I'll keep it.

12:47.650 --> 12:48.340
尽快搞定吧
Let's get this done.

12:48.350 --> 12:51.750
我们得同时盯着两个守卫
We're gonna have to watch both guards simultaneously.

12:52.050 --> 12:53.040
你的房间得腾出来
Your cell should provide

