昨天我找到了个不错的角度
a good view of the guard I saw yesterday.

12:55.250 --> 12:57.440
盯着他做的每件事 并且记下时间
Keep track of everything he does and when he does it.

12:57.450 --> 13:00.250
盯着他的眼睛 看他是否再次往那看
Look for that glare, see if it shows up again.

13:00.950 --> 13:02.250
那你做什么?
What will you be doing?

13:02.250 --> 13:04.250
观察另一个监视塔
Watching the other tower from here.

13:04.650 --> 13:06.340
当我们做事时 得有个人放哨
While our back's turned, we're gonna need a lookout.

13:06.350 --> 13:10.050
好吧 找马宏
Well, find Mahone.

13:10.150 --> 13:11.840
我们不是在耍他么?
I thought we were stringing him along?

13:11.850 --> 13:13.250
让他觉得这是真的
Looks like we're out of string.

13:20.350 --> 13:21.350
蒂博格
Teodoro.

13:22.150 --> 13:22.940
老大
Si, patron?

13:22.950 --> 13:25.250
光干活 没好处 他们有话说么?
What they say about all work and no play, huh?

13:25.450 --> 13:26.440
要放松下
Boy need his rest.

13:26.450 --> 13:28.850
你的手下日程安排得很紧
Your clientele keeps a tight schedule.

13:29.250 --> 13:31.150
我去看看他们有什么需要的
Got to make sure I see to their needs.

13:35.350 --> 13:37.650
我给过你更重要的任务的
I gave you a more important task.

13:38.650 --> 13:40.150
我没听到有什么重要事
But I haven't heard a thing.

13:40.450 --> 13:41.950
那就多加留意点
then listen harder.

13:45.050 --> 13:46.250
我的宝贝
Mi amor.

13:46.450 --> 13:49.350
亲爱的
Ah, mi vida.

